r-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eclean%20energy%20incentives%3C%2Fa%3E%20passed%20through%20the%20Republican-controlled%20House%20of%20Representatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20founders%20and%20investors%20are%20concerned%20about%20the%20knock-on%20impact%20this%20could%20have%20on%20the%20country's%20climate%20tech%20ecosystem%2C%20which%20was%20burgeoning%20under%20the%20Biden-era%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhistory-is-repeating-itself-bidens-ira-luring-european-startups-away-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EInflation%20Reduction%20Act%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20IRA.%20They%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Trump's%20bill%20has%20stifled%20startup%20growth%20ambitions%2C%20pushing%20them%20to%20scale%20back%2C%20pivot%20to%20new%20geographies%2C%20or%20shut%20down%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20a%20graveyard%20of%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20Matthew%20Nordan%2C%20general%20partner%20at%20clean%20tech%20fund%20Azolla%20Ventures%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20a%20lot%20of%20startups%20will%20hibernate%20to%20try%20to%20weather%20the%20storm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarly-stage%20startups%20are%20already%20beginning%20to%20feel%20the%20heat.%20In%20April%2C%20Spencer%20Gore%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Bedrock%20Materials%2C%20a%20sodium-ion%20battery%20startup%2C%20made%20an%20unusual%20announcement%20on%20LinkedIn%3A%20the%20startup%20would%20be%20returning%20most%20of%20its%20%249%20million%20raised%20to%20investors%20and%20ceasing%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20had%20plenty%20of%20operational%20cash%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bit%20was%20the%20techno-economics%20that%20led%20us%20to%20pull%20the%20plug%2C%26quot%3B%20Gore%20told%20BI%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20market%20conditions%20for%20climate%20tech%20startups%20in%20the%20US%20were%20hampered%20by%20waning%20industrial%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fd4d81c2-1901-4175-a884-73d562e0f37b%5C%22%3EStartups%20are%2