a%20metal%20bar%20across%20a%20bridge.%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20final%2024%20players%20play%20Jump%20Rope%20in%20season%20three%2C%20episode%20three.%20Except%20that%20the%20rope%20is%20a%20giant%20rotating%20metal%20bar%2C%20and%20they%20have%20to%20cross%20a%20bridge%20with%20a%20small%20gap%20in%20the%20center%2C%20while%20avoiding%20being%20hit%20by%20the%20bar.%20If%20you%20get%20hit%2C%20you%20fall%20off%20the%20bridge%2C%20which%20is%20very%20high%20in%20the%20air%2C%20and%20die%20on%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20game%20that%20looks%20relatively%20easy%20to%20complete.%20The%20two%20challenges%20are%20having%20enough%20energy%20to%20keep%20jumping%20until%20you%20reach%20the%20end%2C%20and%20timing%20your%20jump%20over%20the%20gap%20in%20the%20middle%20so%20you%20don't%20get%20hit%20by%20the%20bar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20game%20can%20also%20become%20more%20complicated%20based%20on%20the%20players%20around%20you.%20They%20can%20push%2C%20stop%20you%20from%20going%20forward%2C%20or%20tire%20you%20out.%20The%20biggest%20threat%20here%20is%20your%20fellow%20players%2C%20and%20that%20unpredictability%20makes%20this%20game%20much%20harder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETug%20of%20War%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Squid%20Game%20Tug%20of%20War%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F615efa5ba452880019b57216%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETug%20of%20War%20is%20played%20on%20a%20very%20high%20platform.%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20season%20one%2C%20episode%20four%2C%20players%20are%20asked%20to%20form%20teams%20to%20play%20Tug%20of%20War.%20Two%20teams%20are%20taken%20to%20high%20platforms%2C%20chained%20to%20a%20rope%2C%20and%20instructed%20to%20pull%20the%20other%20over%20the%20edge%20to%20their%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20be%20able%20to%20trick%20your%20way%20to%20win%2C%20like%20Gi-hun's%20team%20did%20in%20the%20show%2C%20but%20in%20most%20cases%2C%20the%20game%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20strength%20and%20resilience.%20You%20could%20put%20in%20all%20your%20energy%2C%20but%20if%20you're%20against%20a%20stronger%20team%2C%20there's%20no%20way%20to%20survive%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESix-Legged%20Pentathlon%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222213%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20still%20of%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%26quot%3B%20showing%20four%20men%20and%20one%20woman%20in%20matching%20green%20jumpsuits%2C%20crouching%20together%20while%20their%20feet%20are%20handcuffed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685bf2dff748d8c055f4510a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221245%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20players'%20feet%20are%20handcuffed%20together%20during%20the%20pentathlon.%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20second%20game%20of%20season%20two%2C%20players%20get%20into%20teams%20of%20five%2C%20are%20chained%20together%2C%20and%20have%20to%20race%20another%20team%20around%20a%20circuit.%20But%20at%20five%20sections%20in%20the%20circuit%2C%20the%20team%20has%20to%20stop%20and%20complete%20a%20minigame%20to%20move%20forward.%20A%20different%20member%20has%20to%20do%20each%20challenge.%20You%20are%20shot%20if%20the%20other%20team%20reaches%20the%20finish%20line%20first%2C%20or%20neither%20team%20makes%20it%20to%20the%20finish%20line%20in%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20another%20game%20in%20which%20you%20rely%20on%20your%20fellow%20players%20and%20hope%20your%20allies%20have%20the%20right%20skills%20to%20complete%20the%20five%20tasks.%20Plus%2C%20some%20of%20the%20minigames%20are%20pretty%20hard%2C%20especially%20under%20the%20pressure%20of%20death%2C%20making%20this%20one%20of%20the%20most%20difficult%20games%20to%20survive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHide%20and%20Seek%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20still%20of%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%26quot%3B%20season%20three%2C%20episode%20two%20showing%20a%20man%20wearing%20a%20green%20jumpsuit%2C%20blue%20jersey%20and%20necklace%20with%20a%20key%20on%20it%20looking%20round%20a%20wall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685bf3353d5881a51c1c0930%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDae-ho%20running%20from%20the%20taggers%20in%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%26quot%3B%20season%20three%2C%20episode%20two.%3Cp%3ENo%20Ju-han%20%2F%20Netflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20game%20of%20season%20three%20is%20Hide%20and%20Seek%2C%20in%20which%20players%20are%20randomly%20assigned%20to%20the%20hiding%20or%20seeking%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHiders%20are%20given%20one%20of%20three%20types%20of%20keys%20to%20open%20doors%20and%20have%20to%20either%20survive%20for%2030%20minutes%20or%20find%20the%20exit%20to%20escape.%20Seekers%20are%20given%20knives%20and%20must%20kill%20at%20least%20one%20hider%20to%20pass%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20a%20hider%2C%20your%20chances%20of%20winning%20are%20slim.%20Players%20learn%20halfway%20through%20the%20game%20that%20they%20need%20all%20three%20keys%20to%20get%20through%20all%20the%20doors%20to%20survive%20and%20exit%20the%20game.%20But%20working%20together%20makes%20you%20a%20bigger%20target%20for%20the%20seekers%2C%20and%20the%20exits%20seem%20near%20impossible%20to%20find%20in%20the%20episode%20since%20only%20two%20players%20could%20find%20them.%20Your%20best%20bet%20is%20to%20find%20a%20good%20hiding%20spot%20and%20hope%20you%20can%20fight%20any%20seekers%20that%20find%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20seekers%20get%20an%20advantage%20of%20having%20a%20knife%2C%20but%20a%20weapon%20is%20useless%20if%20you%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20use%20it%2C%20or%20face%20someone%20skilled%20enough%20to%20disarm%20you.%20Hyun-ju%20took%20out%20multiple%20seekers%2C%20and%20she's%20probably%20not%20the%20only%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Hide%20and%20Seek%20doesn't%20have%20the%20highest%20kill%20count%20in%20the%20show%2C%20over%20half%20the%20players%20died%20in%20it%2C%20making%20it%20the%20second%20toughest%20game%20to%20survive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGlass%20Bridge%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222140%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Glass%20Stepping%20arena%20in%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685bf37c85e81483682cb840%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221203%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Glass%20Bridge%20arena%20in%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Glass%20Bridge%2C%20players%20pick%20jerseys%20that%20put%20them%20in%20order%20from%20one%20to%2016%20and%20are%20instructed%20to%20cross%20a%20bridge%20of%20two%20columns%20of%20glass%20platforms.%20The%20catch%20is%20that%20one%20glass%20platform%20in%20each%20row%20is%20too%20weak%20to%20carry%20your%20weight%2C%20leading%20to%20you%20falling%20to%20your%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20cruellest%20game%20of%20the%20entire%20show.%20While%20other%20games%20test%20your%20strength%2C%20intelligence%2C%20agility%2C%20or%20other%20skills%2C%20this%20game%20is%20pure%20chance.%20If%20you're%20anywhere%20in%20the%20top%2012%20spots%2C%20you'll%20have%20to%20be%20the%20luckiest%20person%20in%20the%20world%20to%20get%20to%20the%20end%20without%20stepping%20on%20the%20wrong%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlayers%20at%20the%20back%20have%20to%20hope%20the%20other%20players%20are%20willing%20to%20be%20sacrificial%20lambs%2C%20or%20no%20one%20will%20make%20it%20to%20the%20finish%20line.%20If%20every%20game%20were%20as%20difficult%20as%20this%20one%2C%20no%20one%20would%20be%20left%20alive%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsquid-game-ch